		attunement : true,
		prerequisite : "Requires attunement by a wizard",
		prereqeval : function(v) { return classes.known.wizard ? true : false; },
		description : "This prototype magic orb is made of fine brass & fitted with inner bearings to let portions spin independently. As a bonus action, change into a flat disc or back. Once capable of altering the flow of time, only vestiges of that power remain. Brief glimpses of the future give +2 initiative if not incapacitated. Spellbook with 6 spells, 3 charges (regain 1d3 at dawn), & a spellcasting focus when held. For 1 charge & 1 min, swap a prepared spell for a divination spell within. As a reaction, use 1 charge to add/subtract d4 from visible atk/check/save in 30 ft.",
		descriptionLong : "This prototype magic orb is crafted of the finest brass and fitted with inner bearings, allowing portions to spin independently. As a bonus action, it turns into a disc or back. Once capable of altering the flow of time, the orb's magic has been all but expended. Vestiges of its power remain, giving me the briefest of glimpses into the future. These warnings give me a +2 bonus to initiative if I'm not incapacitated. I can use the disc as my spellbook and, while held, as a spellcasting focus for my wizard spells. It comes with 6 spells and has 3 charges, regaining 1d3 at dawn. I can study the book for 1 minute and expend 1 charge to change one of my prepared spells to a divination spell within. As a reaction when I see a creature within 30 ft roll for an atk, check, or save, I can expend 1 change to add or subtract 1d4 from the roll. This happens after the roll but before the roll's effects are applied.",
