		source : [["AL","PO"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		magicItemTable : "G",
		description : "This slightly tattered black cloak has a strong scent of mushrooms and mildew, despite its otherwise clean appearance.The cloak grants adv. on Stealth (Dex) checks. In dim light or darkness, I can use the cloak to fly (40 ft speed) and once per dawn turn into a bat as if casting Polymorph but retaining my INT, WIS, and CHA. To fly I must grip the cloak's edges with both hands.",
