		description : "This metallic blue bowl is ~1 ft in diameter & 1/2 as deep. It weighs 3 pounds, holds ~3 gallons, & shifts & swirls slowly when examined. The bowl's command phrase is inscribed in silver Aquan glyphs along its inside lip: “From the Plane of Water, I wrench thee; From the Archomental, I bind thee”. Once per dawn while it's filled with water, I can say the bowl's command phrase as an action & summon a water elemental as if casting Conjure Elemental.",
