		description : "This piece of the Dawnbringer's gear shift is a segmented tube of adamantine. I can manipulate the notched knobs & numbered joints along its length to deploy an array of screwdriver heads & tool bits. While holding the tube, I gain a +1 bonus to spell atk rolls & saving throw DCs of my artificer spells. As an action, I can transform it into a set of artisan's tools. Once per day as an action, I can choose a cantrip I don't know & cast it as an artificer cantrip for 8 hrs.",
