		description : "The rim of this circular mirror is engraved with Draconic letters that spell out the following in Loross: “Look into me & I will show you what has been.” As an action once per dawn, I can gaze into the mirror while thinking of a specific object or creature. The mirror shows scenes from the target's past for up to 1 minute. The information is accurate but random, cryptic & presented in no particular order.",
