		description : "With green plumage & a golden quill & shaft, this oversized feather is considered a good luck charm. Thora's grandfather told her it came from a magnificent gentle griffon that roamed the skies around Forheim. As an action while outdoors, I can touch it to an unoccupied space on the ground. The token disappears & a 60-ft tall nonmagical oak tree springs into its place. The trunk has a 5-ft diameter & its branches at the top spread out in a 20-ft radius.",
