			source : [["AL","CCC"]],
			magicItemTable : "G",
			description : "As an action, I can speak the command word & throw one or both of these gold statuettes to an unoccupied space w/i 60 ft, where each becomes a lion for 1 hr, until I repeat command or it reaches 0 hp. The lions that appear are twinned pairs of contrast coloration. One white w/ black stripes, one black w/ white stripes. They're friendly, understand my languages, & obey my commands.",
			descriptionLong : "As an action, I can speak the command word and throw one or both of these gold statuettes of a lion to an unoccupied space within 60 ft, where each becomes a lion for up to 1 hr, until I use an action to repeat the command word, or it reaches 0 hp. The lions that appear are twinned pairs of opposite colouration. One white w/ black stripes, the other black w/ white stripes. They are friendly to me and my allies, understands my languages, and obeys my spoken commands. If I issue no commands, the creature defends itself but takes no other actions. When it reverts back to a figurine, it can't be used again for 7 days.",
