		rarity : "common",
		magicItemTable : "?",
		description : "These knee-high leather boots are stitched with thick threads of plant fiber that spell out 'false form' and 'thousand faces' in Druidic script. Only humanoids can wear them. While wearing the boots, I can choose to leave tracks like those of another kind of humanoid of my size.",
