		description : "These boots are embroidered with the image of a mountain venting a large plume of white smoke. While worn I'm fluent in Gnomish. As a bonus action, click their heels together to double my walking speed & give opportunity attacks against me disadv. Effect ended with another bonus action. The boots can be used for 10 min. total, recharging after a long rest.",
