		description : "While I wear these slippers, I can move up, down, & across vertical surfaces & upside-down along ceilings, while leaving my hands free. I have a climbing speed equal to my walking speed. The slippers don't let me move this way on a slippery surface, i.e. one covered by ice or oil. As an action, I can cause my voice to carry up to 300 ft until my next turn ends. When used this way, my voice gains a tinge of malevolence regardless of the words.",
