		magicItemTable : "B",
		description : "This pink shimmery jellyfish was beautifully preserved by Jilly Stillwater and is perfectly odorless. The long tendrils serve as a scarf when I use it as a hat. While worn, I can use an action to cast the Comprehend Languages spell at will. I can also use the imbued illusion magic to alter its appearance in minor ways.",
