		description : "Made from the bone of a colossal ancient white tiger, the war horn creates a tiger's roar that echoes across the planes. It also roars warnings, granting me +2 to initiative while not incapacitated. As an action once per 7 days, I can blow the horn to summon 2d4+2 warrior spirits within 60 ft. These Berserkers disappear after 1 hr or at 0 hp. They're friendly & follow my commands.",
