		description : "As bonus action, I can blow this brass horn to stop being frightened & gain adv. on saves against fear until my next turn. When activated, the war rune glows purple & the horn plays the worship song of random god (1: Garl Glittergold, 2: Sune, 3: Lathander, 4: Valkur, 5: Bane, 6: Jergal, 7: Talos, 8: Torm). Once per day when blown, I can also give chosen creatures in 30 ft +1 AC until my next turn.",
