		source : [["AL","FR-DC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		magicItemTable : "G",
		description : "This amulet is crafted from the tooth of a green dragon named Azdraka, who terrorized the High Road south of Neverwinter and was slain by Lady Tanamere Alagondar. I can speak Draconic when it's on my person. While worn, I'm immune to the poisoned condition and poison damage.",
		descriptionFull : "This amulet is crafted from the tooth of a green dragon named Azdraka, who once terrorized the High Road south of Neverwinter and was slain by Lady Tanamere Alagondar.\n   " + toUni("Language") + ". The bearer can speak and understand draconic while the item is on the bearer’s person.\n   This delicate silver chain has a brilliant-cut black gem pendant. While you wear it, poisons have no effect on you. You are immune to the poisoned condition and have immunity to poison damage.",
