		description : "This large seawater pearl was worn as a pendant by Mar-Itez. It was originally pure white but has been stained red & can't be cleaned by any means. When attuning, I hear a soft but determined whisper: “I shed my blood, I pour it as the moment comes. So may we be gilded by a reflection of the heaven's newlyborn light.” Once per dawn as an action, bleed on the pearl & speak its command word to regain 1 expended spell slot. If the slot was above 3rd lvl, the new slot is 3rd lvl.",
