				"A sphere sheds dim light in 30-ft radius, its damage depends on the number created:",
				" \u2022 1 sphere: 4d12;    \u2022 2 spheres: 5d4;    \u2022 3 spheres: 2d6;    \u2022 4 spheres: 2d4"
