		magicItemTable : "H",
		description : "This thick 3 ft \xD7 5 ft down-filled comforter is embroidered with the horizon of Idlip. It's enchanted to grant pleasant dreams \u0026 whisper warnings, adding +2 initiative unless incapacitated. I can speak its command word as an action to make it hover \u0026 fly. The comforter moves according to my spoken directions if I'm within 30 ft. It has a flying speed of 80 ft \u0026 can carry up to 400 lb. If carrying more than 200 lb, its flying speed is reduced to 40 ft.",
