		source : [["AL","FR-DC"]],
		rarity : "common",
		description : "This wand has 3 charges, regained at dawn. As an action, I can wave the wand & use 1 charge to create orchestral music that's audible to a range of 60 ft & ends when I stop waving it. If I use its last charge, I roll a d20. On a 1, a sad tuba sound plays as the wand crumbles to dust. While on my person, I can speak Deep Speech.",
		descriptionFull : "This wand has 3 charges. While holding the wand, you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges and create orchestral music by waving it around. The music can be heard out to a range of 60 feet and ends when you stop waving the wand.\n   The wand regains all expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, a sad tuba sound plays as the wand crumbles to dust and is destroyed.\n   " + toUni("Language") + ". While this wand is on your person, can read and understand deep speech as you hear whispers in the back of your mind.",
