		source : [["AL:SA","11A"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		magicItemTable : "G",
		description : "This crystalline wand appears as a spiral-shaped waterspout and gives off a haunting melody when used. It has 7 charges, regaining 1d6+1 at dawn. As an action, spend 1 charge to have a thin blue ray hit a visible creature in 60 ft. The target makes a DC 15 Con save or is paralyzed for 1 min. It can repeat the save at the end of each turn. 5% chance the wand is destroyed when last charge used (1 on a d20).",
