		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "common",
		magicItemTable : "?",
		description : "This wand crafted from an illithid tentacle feels like it's squirming in my hand. Anyone staring at it for a minute hears an ominous voice in their head: “WARNING: best used on strangers & loved ones.” It has 3 charges, regained at dawn. As an action, spend 1 charge & target a visible humanoid in 30 ft. The target must pass a DC 10 Charisma save or smile for 1 min. 5% chance of turning into a wand of scowls when last charged used.",
