		magicItemTable : "?",
		description : "This branch from the Awakening Fruit tree was empowered with magic by Ditse Mare. It has 3 charges, regained at dawn, & whispers warnings, granting me +2 to initiative unless incapacitated. As an action, say the words “asim kilig”, spend 1 charge & target a visible humanoid in 30 ft. They must pass a DC 10 Charisma save or smile for 1 min, face puckering like they ate a sweet-sour-citrus fruit. If the last charged used, roll a d20. On a 1, it becomes a wand of scowls.",
